        <body>
            <div>
                <opener>
                    <dateline><hi rendition="#mPrint">
                            <hi rendition="#mPrint"><pb n=""/>Saint Peter's Square.
                            Manchester,</hi></hi> 1 October <hi rendition="#mPrint"><hi rendition="#mPrint">186</hi></hi>7</dateline>
                    <salute>Dear Lomax</salute>
                </opener>
                <p/>
                
                <p>I have put Ross’ three Hunters in the Guardian &amp; Courier of today. Their
                    prices are as follows</p>
                <p>
                    <table rows="3" cols="2">
                        <row>
                            <cell>Brown Horses</cell>
                            <cell>£ 120</cell>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <cell>Chesnut Mare</cell>
                            <cell>” 140</cell>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <cell>Bay –</cell>
                            <cell>” 80</cell>
                        </row>
                    </table>
                </p>
                <p> If you can meet with a purchaser I shall be very much obliged –</p>
                <p>Yours truly</p>
                <p> WHenderson</p>
                <p>Lawson knows all about <hi rendition="#u">them</hi> &amp; has Ross’ instructions
                    –</p>
            </div>
        </body>
